{
  "stem": "21582.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because to us, as children, there was a mixture of fear and a mixture of adventure.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "War was like a game.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was out there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It, it, it, it-- it's not real.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So yes, there was an awareness and, and the unrest of, of, of outbreaks of hooliganism.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of that was very, very clear and very much part of our lives, just as much as the joyous parts were.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And really, very much in my life is like, like balancing on a very, very sharp edge of wonderfulness and horror.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] When you think, think back to those days, do you, by any chance, recall some of your images of, of Hitler and what  the Nazis were doing?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, what was your understanding?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- I-- I'm talking now about pre-war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The news that came, this getting ready to invade, the justifications or the rationalizations, the exclamations, the declarations of superiority, the put-downs of not just Jewish people, but-- everyone else was a secondary citizen.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jews were below anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Poles were dirty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The English were something else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But everyone-- there, there was a great-- I think that the build-up towards all of the actions that the Germans did that came out in the news and, and, and the justifications that surely they had a right because they needed the lebensraum, the room that, that they lost.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were all kinds during the First World War.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were all kinds of justifications and rationalizations and signs of aggression that we were aware of in the news.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it still was out there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It still was not, not real.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was, you know-- and then there were all kinds of preparations by the Polish people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were all kinds of slogans on the radio.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
